      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数年後",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "莉央にコネ採用を頼む",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_dangerous-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 68.9666712443
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh008.wav",
              "text": "莉央さん、お願いだ！\n俺を採用するように上に掛け合ってくれ！",
              "startTime": 68.9666712443,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 0
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh009.wav",
              "text": "金欠で就職が決まらないとマジでヤバいんだ\nなぁ、頼むよ。昔のよしみでさ",
              "startTime": 73.7333379109,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-rio002.wav",
              "text": "はぁ……\nどうして私はこんな情けないやつと……",
              "startTime": 80.9666697184,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-rio003.wav",
              "text": "いいわ\n貴方のことは人事に話しておいてあげる\nそのかわり、一つだけ約束して",
              "startTime": 86.3333348592,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-rio004.wav",
              "text": "二度と私に話し掛けないで",
              "startTime": 95.4333328247,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 3466.659672999995
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh010.wav",
              "text": "（こうして俺は、莉央さんのコネで無事に\n再就職することが出来た）",
              "startTime": 98.1333379109,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh011.wav",
              "text": "（その後も何度か莉央さんを見かけたが\n冷めた瞳で睨まれるといたたまれなくなって\n二度と話し掛けることは出来なかった）",
              "startTime": 102.9666676838,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "莉央にコネ採用を頼まない",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "choice_selection",
              "choices": [
                {
                  "text": "金を貸してくれ！",
                  "route": []
                },
                {
                  "text": "俺と結婚してくれ！",
                  "route": []
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh012.wav",
              "text": "久しぶりです、莉央さん\n……一つ聞いてもいいですか？\n莉央さんは今、幸せですか",
              "startTime": 112.6333343505,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_meeting-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 122.3333394367
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-rio005.wav",
              "text": "ええ。この会社は私の働きを高く評価して\nくれるわ。ここでならやりたかった仕事が\n出来る。私は今、幸せよ",
              "startTime": 122.3333394367,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh013.wav",
              "text": "そうですか。それなら良かった",
              "startTime": 134.0999969481,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rio",
              "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-rio006.wav",
              "text": "じゃあ、私は仕事があるからもう行くわね\nさようなら、{user}君",
              "startTime": 137.7333282469,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
                  "delay": 5618.797969799999
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh014.wav",
              "text": "さようなら、莉央さん……",
              "startTime": 145.1,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 148.2999975841
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_serious-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 149.5999975841
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh015.wav",
              "text": "はぁ……これからどうしよう……\n収入ゼロ、貯金もゼロで\n一体どうやって生きていけば……",
              "startTime": 150.4666646321,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 8999.997997099996
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 158.6060954411
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-rui001.wav",
              "text": "あら？　もしかして……\nやっぱり！　こんな所で会うなんて奇遇ね",
              "startTime": 159.2999959309,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 165.4666615803
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh016.wav",
              "text": "瑠依！？　久しぶりだな\n会うのは会社が倒産して以来か？",
              "startTime": 165.4666615803,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "rui",
              "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-rui002.wav",
              "text": "ええ、{user}君は\n元気そうね。会えて嬉しいわ",
              "startTime": 170.9999949137,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh017.wav",
              "text": "俺も嬉しいよ\nこうして会えたのも何かの縁だ。瑠依――",
              "startTime": 175.4333302815,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 180.2424459775
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 1.1666666667
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
