      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh002.wav",
      "text": "（優秀な莉央さんはヘッドハンティングで\n大企業に転職出来たが\n俺は再就職に失敗して無職になり……）",
      "startTime": 11.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh003.wav",
      "text": "（俺と莉央さんはすれ違うことが多くなって\n関係を修復出来ないまま自然消滅という形で\n二人の関係はあっさり終わってしまった）",
      "startTime": 18.7333332062,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_preentrance-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "preentrance-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.7333361308
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh004.wav",
      "text": "今度こそ再就職しようと\n中途採用の面接を受けに来たけど……\n今日の面接は手応えがまるでなかったな",
      "startTime": 28.7333361308,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh005.wav",
      "text": "これは絶対不採用だよ……\n貯金も底をついて、明日からどうやって\n生活したらいいんだ",
      "startTime": 37.6000027974,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8199.997202599996
