    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh006.wav",
      "text": "莉央さん！？　どうしてここに……\nあ、この会社、莉央さんが転職した会社か\n応募し過ぎて社名すらあやふやだった……",
      "startTime": 50.1000045776,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
