      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03/sud_vo_adv_love_2603_08_03-koh018.wav",
      "text": "頼む瑠依！　一生のお願いだ！\n黙って俺に金を貸してくれ！",
      "startTime": 182.1333302815,
      "sfxList": [
        {
